 their fun on the island. Everyone knows not to disturb him with work during this time but yet someone does anyway and he has to address it. This is related to what's happened to the last several stories. That's how it ties together. It's definitely rated M for Mature which I know won't be everyone's cup of tea and I'm fine with that. But I also think I could write it without needing to go that route as well. Like it would be in addition to. Similar to what I said I'd do with the 'Training Session' Novelette.¬†

